com.google.maps.android.geojson

Class GeoJsonPolygonStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.google.maps.android.geojson.GeoJsonPolygonStyle

  • public class GeoJsonPolygonStyle
extends java.util.Observable
    A class that allows for GeoJsonPolygon objects to be styled and for these styles to be translated into a PolygonOptions object. PolygonOptions docs for more details about the options.
